            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%206%3A1-7%3A25%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EIsaiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Cleansing%20and%20Call%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20was%20in%20the%20year%20King%20Uzziah%20died%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20King%20Uzziah%20died%20in%20740%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20that%20I%20saw%20the%20Lord.%20He%20was%20sitting%20on%20a%20lofty%20throne%2C%20and%20the%20train%20of%20his%20robe%20filled%20the%20Temple.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EAttending%20him%20were%20mighty%20seraphim%2C%20each%20having%20six%20wings.%20With%20two%20wings%20they%20covered%20their%20faces%2C%20with%20two%20they%20covered%20their%20feet%2C%20and%20with%20two%20they%20flew.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20were%20calling%20out%20to%20each%20other%2C%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BHoly%2C%20holy%2C%20holy%20is%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20whole%20earth%20is%20filled%20with%20his%20glory!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_4%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3ETheir%20voices%20shook%20the%20Temple%20to%20its%20foundations%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20building%20was%20filled%20with%20smoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_5%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20I%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%26%23x2019%3Bs%20all%20over!%20I%20am%20doomed%2C%20for%20I%20am%20a%20sinful%20man.%20I%20have%20filthy%20lips%2C%20and%20I%20live%20among%20a%20people%20with%20filthy%20lips.%20Yet%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20King%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_6%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20one%20of%20the%20seraphim%20flew%20to%20me%20with%20a%20burning%20coal%20he%20had%20taken%20from%20the%20altar%20with%20a%20pair%20of%20tongs.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_7%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20touched%20my%20lips%20with%20it%20and%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BSee%2C%20this%20coal%20has%20touched%20your%20lips.%20Now%20your%20guilt%20is%20removed%2C%20and%20your%20sins%20are%20forgiven.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_8%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20I%20heard%20the%20Lord%20asking%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhom%20should%20I%20send%20as%20a%20messenger%20to%20this%20people%3F%20Who%20will%20go%20for%20us%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EI%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BHere%20I%20am.%20Send%20me.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_9%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20he%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYes%2C%20go%2C%20and%20say%20to%20this%20people%2C%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x2018%3BListen%20carefully%2C%20but%20do%20not%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWatch%20closely%2C%20but%20learn%20nothing.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_10%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EHarden%20the%20hearts%20of%20these%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EPlug%20their%20ears%20and%20shut%20their%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThat%20way%2C%20they%20will%20not%20see%20with%20their%20eyes%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Enor%20hear%20with%20their%20ears%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Enor%20understand%20with%20their%20hearts%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20turn%20to%20me%20for%20healing.%26%23x201D%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A9-10%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20version%20reads%20%3Cem%3EAnd%20he%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BGo%20and%20say%20to%20this%20people%2C%20%2F%20%26%23x2018%3BWhen%20you%20hear%20what%20I%20say%2C%20you%20will%20not%20understand.%20%2F%20When%20you%20see%20what%20I%20do%2C%20you%20will%20not%20comprehend.%26%23x2019%3B%20%2F%20For%20the%20hearts%20of%20these%20people%20are%20hardened%2C%20%2F%20and%20their%20ears%20cannot%20hear%2C%20and%20they%20have%20closed%20their%20eyes%26%23x2014%3B%20%2F%20so%20their%20eyes%20cannot%20see%2C%20%2F%20and%20their%20ears%20cannot%20hear%2C%20%2F%20and%20their%20hearts%20cannot%20understand%2C%20%2F%20and%20they%20cannot%20turn%20to%20me%20and%20let%20me%20heal%20them.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20Compare%20Matt%2013%3A14-15%3B%20Mark%204%3A12%3B%20Luke%208%3A10%3B%20Acts%2028%3A26-27.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_11%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20I%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLord%2C%20how%20long%20will%20this%20go%20on%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EAnd%20he%20replied%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BUntil%20their%20towns%20are%20empty%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Etheir%20houses%20are%20deserted%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20whole%20country%20is%20a%20wasteland%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_12%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3Euntil%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20sent%20everyone%20away%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20entire%20land%20of%20Israel%20lies%20deserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_6_13%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20even%20a%20tenth%26%23x2014%3Ba%20remnant%26%23x2014%3Bsurvive%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eit%20will%20be%20invaded%20again%20and%20burned.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EBut%20as%20a%20terebinth%20or%20oak%20tree%20leaves%20a%20stump%20when%20it%20is%20cut%20down%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20stump%20will%20be%20a%20holy%20seed.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_7_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Message%20for%20Ahaz%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Ahaz%2C%20son%20of%20Jotham%20and%20grandson%20of%20Uzziah%2C%20was%20king%20of%20Judah%2C%20King%20Rezin%20of%20Syria%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EAram%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%207%3A2%2C%204%2C%205%2C%208.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20Pekah%20son%20of%20Remaliah%2C%20the%20king%20of%20Israel%2C%20set%20out%20to%20attack%20Jerusalem.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_7_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20news%20had%20come%20to%20the%20royal%20court%20of%20Judah%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BSyria%20is%20allied%20with%20Israel%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EEphraim%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20referring%20to%20the%20northern%20kingdom%20of%20Israel%3B%20also%20in%207%3A5%2C%208%2C%209%2C%2017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20against%20us!%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20the%20hearts%20of%20the%20king%20and%20his%20people%20trembled%20with%20fear%2C%20like%20trees%20shaking%20in%20a%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_7_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Isaiah%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BTake%20your%20son%20Shear-jashub%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A3a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3EShear-jashub%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20%26%23x201C%3BA%